                    "text": {
                      "value": "<p style=color:black><i>A part of the Perpetual Planet Initiative, the Rolex Awards for Enterprise support exceptional individuals with innovative projects in areas as diverse as creating technologies that improve lives, saving endangered ecosystems, protecting the oceans, exploring new frontiers on the planet, or pioneering advances in science and health.</i></p>"
