                    "descriptionText": {
                      "value": "Indonesian entrepreneur Denica Riadini-Flesch is changing the future for rural craftswomen through her farm-to-closet clothing brand. She pays them a fair living wage for traditionally crafted clothing made from materials grown using regenerative agriculture, thereby breathing new life into the country’s rich heritage."
